body_html:
What verison of tensorflow source are you using? i.e. run

git describe

from the root of your tensorflow sources?

Are you able to build a working whl from source in general?
https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_sources

If that doesn't work, Try to build TensorFlow with only CPU suppport. If that can be made to work then try flowers with the cpu version.

body:
What verison of tensorflow source are you using? i.e. run
```
git describe 
```
from the root of your tensorflow sources?

Are you able to build a working whl from source in general?
https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_sources

If that doesn't work, Try to build TensorFlow with only CPU suppport. If that can be made to work then try flowers with the cpu version.
